<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='153:179'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-1a' );" name="003-1a" class="pb">[003-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='179:187'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='187:208'>　詩故卷三　　　　　　　明　朱謀㙔　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='208:211'>王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='211:234'>黍離閔宗周也何以閔閔東遷之失謀也西周政令所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='234:257'>　以能行乎諸侯者非徒文武成康之徳亦以地勢險</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='257:280'>　固足食足兵可以東制諸侯之命耳幽王雖死驪山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='280:303'>　犬戎無盤據豐鄗之理乃因一敗遽爾東遷有識之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='303:326'>　士於其行也痛悼失圖故賦此詩黍稷離離下垂而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='326:352'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-1b' );" name="003-1b" class="pb">[003-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='352:375'>　碩猶有憂者中心思惟而傾其首也陳平深憂吕氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='375:398'>　之亂陸賈入坐而平不見賈是其驗矣非故宫廟盡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='398:407'>　為禾黍之場也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='407:430'>君子于役刺平王也非刺平也傷周弱也西周之世大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='430:453'>　夫非無行役也出有四牡皇華之勞入有杕杜魚麗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='453:476'>　之燕人皆以為盛典而寵榮之也逮夫東遷政在諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='476:499'>　侯而天子之公卿大夫奔走聘問無有寧歳昔時燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='499:522'>　勞之典廢矣大夫之妻賦此而孔子録之正以傷周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='522:548'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-2a' );" name="003-2a" class="pb">[003-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='548:569'>　室之日微耳不知其期曷至哉七言通為一句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='569:592'>君子陽陽閔周也非閔周也君子為貧而仕卑官也所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='592:615'>　謂卑官則籥師也房者俎也王公立飫則有房烝魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='615:638'>　頌亦稱籩豆大房萬舞洋洋盖房俎籥舞俱在堂下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='638:661'>　故曰招我由房非路寢之房也敖者燕舞之位樂記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='661:670'>　所謂綴兆是矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='670:679'>揚之水刺平王也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='679:702'>中谷有蓷閔周也非閔周也凶年饑饉女子自傷困窮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='702:728'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-2b' );" name="003-2b" class="pb">[003-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='728:751'>　不能賙其母家也蓷名茺蔚亦名益母因舉益母而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='751:774'>　知其為念母家因遇人之艱難而知其為女子也昔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='774:792'>　曾子覩益母而興悲殆有感于是詩乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='792:815'>兔爰閔周也非閔周也君子哀時命也兔狡於避禍雉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='815:838'>　拙於自免二物小大相等故古人並舉之内則雉兔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='838:861'>　皆有芼孟子雉兔者往焉是也兔以喻小人雉以自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='861:878'>　喻爰爰緩意謂能以狡自緩其死也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='878:901'>葛藟王族刺平王也非刺也諷王親其族類以自立也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='901:927'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-3a' );" name="003-3a" class="pb">[003-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='927:950'>　鄭伯朝周王不禮焉周桓公諫曰我周之東遷晉鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='950:973'>　焉依善鄭以勸來者猶懼不蔇况不禮焉鄭不來矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='973:984'>　葛藟之諷殆為是乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='984:1007'>采葛懼䜛也葛善攀附蕭艾並善蕪穢皆喻小人之黨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1007:1030'>　也好䜛之人醜正惡直唯依阿鄙賤之是近故我一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1030:1049'>　日不見遽已相忘不啻三月三歳之久矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1049:1072'>大車刺周大夫也非刺周大夫也商者之婦寄其夫也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1072:1095'>　周之地狹民衆多賈齊魯梁楚仰機利而逐末業輕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1095:1121'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-3b' );" name="003-3b" class="pb">[003-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1121:1144'>　去家室其妻重于改適故賦此寄焉大車牛車任載</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1144:1167'>　者非大夫車也毳衣毛褐將車者之服非毳冕也我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1167:1190'>　見毳衣之人數將牛車而來子獨不歸疑棄我矣我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1190:1213'>　欲他奔猶畏子之或來有所不敢唯誓死以待之此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1213:1224'>　其俗猶有足稱者焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1224:1247'>丘中有麻思賢也非思賢也商者荅大車也子言我久</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1247:1270'>　不歸資生無所然丘園之中有麻可績有麥可食有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1270:1293'>　李可殽也凡此三物足以留子我亦將施施而來與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1293:1319'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-4a' );" name="003-4a" class="pb">[003-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1319:1342'>　子共之矣貽我佩玖者感其異室同穴之誓寶重其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1342:1365'>　言如瓊玖之可佩服也録此二詩見周俗忠厚尚禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1365:1371'>　有如此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1371:1394'>鄭詩二十一篇始武莊終忽突皆國事也其它亦多賢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1394:1417'>　人君子之詞而宋世之儒誤釋放鄭聲一語遂去小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1417:1440'>　序盡以淫奔目之夫詩非聲也聲非詩也措諸文詞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1440:1463'>　是為詩被諸管絃音律是為聲鄭音好濫而淫志者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1463:1479'>　故仲尼放之豈緇衣仲子諸詩乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1479:1505'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-4b' );" name="003-4b" class="pb">[003-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1505:1528'>緇衣美武公也周人之詞也桓公以鄭伯入相于周死</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1528:1551'>　犬戎之難武公繼為平王司徒世善其職故周人歌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1551:1574'>　之適謂安適其館舎也若謂廩餼之不繼而欲還我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1574:1597'>　將授子以粲焉是皆勉留之意也蓆有四訓毛傳訓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1597:1620'>　大韓詩訓儲許慎訓為廣多唯朱傳訓為安舒者得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1620:1624'>　之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1624:1647'>將仲子刺莊公也莊公志在除段欲其積釁累瑕而後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1647:1670'>　動鄭人已知之審矣故託為公拒祭仲之詞以杞桑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1670:1696'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-5a' );" name="003-5a" class="pb">[003-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1696:1715'>　與檀比叔段不欲即折喻欲待其自斃耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1715:1738'>叔于田刺莊公也非刺莊也著叔段之得衆也于田取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1738:1761'>　禽也里塗曰巷里巷者細民所居叔段處京既有人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1761:1784'>　民社稷之寄宜求良士以輔弼之今乃獨為里巷小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1784:1796'>　人所好是速亡之道耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1796:1819'>大叔于田刺莊公也非刺莊也著叔段之繕其甲兵也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1819:1836'>　稱大叔者左傳所謂京城太叔是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1836:1859'>清人刺文公也髙克所將者清邑之兵也曰彭曰消曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1859:1885'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-5b' );" name="003-5b" class="pb">[003-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1885:1908'>　軸三境之地師所次也駟介者兵車之駟也車上載</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1908:1931'>　兵獨稱二矛者舉兵之最長者以該之左旋右抽者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1931:1954'>　三軍之左右皆潰散而歸清邑也獨髙克所將中軍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1954:1959'>　在爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1959:1982'>羔裘刺朝也非刺朝也美賢大夫也古者君狐裘大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1982:2005'>　緇衣羔裘以羊性剛直可尚羔又柔澤温煖可親加</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2005:2028'>　以豹飾又表其武三徳具備故曰三英語此大夫之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2028:2051'>　徳足稱此裘也舍命不渝守死善道也豈叔詹子皮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2051:2077'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-6a' );" name="003-6a" class="pb">[003-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2077:2083'>　之徒與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2083:2106'>遵大路思君子也非思君子也賢者以道去國也遵大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2106:2129'>　路其去明也寁者速也不寁故者與聞政事已久志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2129:2152'>　好浹洽非新知比也此盖託為挽留者之詞嚴粲謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2152:2175'>　鄭莊公殺弟幽母射王中肩悖逆已甚君子去之殆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2175:2181'>　有為哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2181:2204'>女曰雞鳴刺不悦徳也非刺也賢夫婦交相警戒之詞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2204:2227'>　也稱士女始婚者也弋鳬雁丈夫之事也調五味中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2227:2253'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-6b' );" name="003-6b" class="pb">[003-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2253:2276'>　饋之職也琴瑟静好養徳之具也宜其酒饌以奉賓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2276:2299'>　客所以成徳也古者子事父母左右佩用紛帨刀礪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2299:2322'>　大觽小觽金燧玦捍管遰木燧謂之雜佩非珩璜琚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2322:2345'>　瑀之屬也宜言飲酒與子偕老者言調和滋味佐酒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2345:2363'>　以勞慰其夫願執此道偕老而不廢也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2363:2386'>有女同車刺忽也何刺乎追刺之也忽以不昏于齊遂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2386:2405'>　無大援終見逐于鄭國人追刺其失圖也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2405:2428'>山有扶蘇刺忽也何所刺之刺其闇于任人而致亂亡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2428:2454'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-7a' );" name="003-7a" class="pb">[003-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2454:2477'>　也扶蘇猶言扶疎木相扶而植者如所謂扶桑扶栘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2477:2500'>　扶栁之類非小木也扶蘇喬松宜在髙山比賢人君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2500:2523'>　子宜處顯位荷華游龍宜生下隰比狂狡之童宜備</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2523:2540'>　奔走今所庸顯者莫非狂狡故刺之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2540:2563'>蘀兮刺忽也非刺也鄭人思黜突而納忽也忽以世子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2563:2586'>　踐位正矣宋人乃使祭仲立突而逐忽鄭人故不義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2586:2609'>　突而賦此詩託風之隕蘀以見志叔兮伯兮謂大國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2609:2628'>　也安得大國秉義納忽我當起而應之矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2628:2654'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-7b' );" name="003-7b" class="pb">[003-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2654:2677'>狡童刺忽也非刺忽也刺突之與雍糾為謀以殺祭仲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2677:2700'>　也雍糾洩謀于妻而見殺突以出奔所謂狡童其謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2700:2716'>　糾乎惜其不與老成謀之而僨事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2716:2739'>褰裳思見正也突與忽争國更出更入不復以禮義相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2739:2762'>　先故思得大國以正其名分焉狂童之狂也且謂大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2762:2785'>　國不來正之者直以突之狂而無禮不足正耳絶望</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2785:2791'>　之詞也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2791:2814'>丰刺亂也非刺亂也志悔恨也鄭女盖有矜其族類門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2814:2840'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-8a' );" name="003-8a" class="pb">[003-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2840:2863'>　地已許嫁而中悔者既而愆期無歸還自咎恨耳悔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2863:2886'>　婚之志未必親迎之際曰巷曰堂直託喻耳叔兮伯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2886:2905'>　兮不一人者已失所婚覬他姓之我求也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2905:2928'>東門之墠刺亂也非刺亂也惜狷介者之遯世也除地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2928:2951'>　町町然者謂之墠陂陀不平而可種藝者之謂阪踐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2951:2974'>　謂樹栗之有行列也東門之墠其阪有茹藘焉是其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2974:2997'>　人所居之地也樹栗林然有行是其家室所在也第</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2997:3010'>　絶人避世不可得而見耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3010:3036'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-8b' );" name="003-8b" class="pb">[003-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3036:3059'>風雨思君子也喪亂之中樂見秉徳不回之士也風雨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3059:3082'>　凄凄以氣言風雨瀟瀟以聲言雞鳴不已語雞能司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3082:3097'>　晨不為風雨晦㝠而廢其鳴也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3097:3120'>子衿刺學校廢也非刺學校廢也朋友失好者之相責</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3120:3143'>　讓也城闕都㑹之所非遐荒也以細故而斷平生之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3143:3156'>　歡遂不相見是誠絶我矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3156:3176'>揚之水閔忽之無忠臣也非閔忽也諷聽䜛也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3176:3199'>出其東門閔亂也非閔亂也遯世者荅東門之墠之詞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3199:3225'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-9a' );" name="003-9a" class="pb">[003-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3225:3248'>　也鄭俗尚縞故僑札相見贈以縞帶此云縞衣綦巾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3248:3271'>　已之室也荼者苦菜河北最蕃今俗呼為舒菜如荼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3271:3294'>　猶言如雲喻女子之衆非喪服之謂也出城闉者盖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3294:3306'>　相率郊外墦間之祭耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3306:3329'>野有蔓草思遇時也非思遇時思其治也有道之世俊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3329:3352'>　桀在位野無奥草矣此何時乎君子在野田卒汚萊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3352:3375'>　國何當而治乎曰蔓草零露知田野之不辟也有美</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3375:3398'>　一人邂逅于草露之區知君子之在野也昔六卿餞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3398:3424'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-9b' );" name="003-9b" class="pb">[003-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3424:3447'>　韓宣子子齹首賦此詩宣子善之曰吾有望矣豈男</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3447:3458'>　女思不期而㑹者哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3458:3481'>溱洧刺亂也非刺亂也志其俗之荒于游觀也韓詩傅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3481:3504'>　稱鄭國之俗三月上已桃花水下之時士女競出溱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3504:3527'>　洧之上執蘭招魂續魄以祓不祥是則漢世以來上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3527:3550'>　已祓除所昉也蕳草一名都梁髙四五尺性善殺蠱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3550:3573'>　故士女秉之以祓不祥耳勺藥即今牡丹華于上已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3573:3596'>　之時中州等之荆榛折華以贈亦士女夫婦之相愛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3596:3623'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-10a' );" name="003-10a" class="pb">[003-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3623:3638'>　非妄一男子見所悦而贈之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3638:3641'>齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3641:3664'>雞鳴思賢妃也非思賢妃也盖賢夫人能警戒以成其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3664:3687'>　君之徳也雞三號卒明而後蠅蚋交作已乃日出東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3687:3710'>　方是為黎明久之日光被物是為大明朝㑹者雞鳴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3710:3733'>　來集别色始入其時蒼蠅交作而有聲自此以往日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3733:3756'>　亦出矣故曰匪東方則明日出之光傳寫之誤遂作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3756:3779'>　月出故説者費詞而難通考之周史武王女適齊為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3779:3806'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-10b' );" name="003-10b" class="pb">[003-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3806:3829'>　乙公夫人乙公生癸公癸公之子為哀公以荒淫誅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3829:3844'>　此所謂賢者其乙公之王姬乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3844:3867'>還刺荒也何荒乎刺禽荒也哀公好田無厭國人化之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3867:3890'>　遂以成俗狼似犬而大銳頭細腰髙前廣後得人物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3890:3913'>　則殘其軀體而食之出必兩頭相恃猛捷貪忍雖用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3913:3936'>　兵者莫能免今曰並驅而從兩狼信便捷矣肩與豜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3936:3945'>　通田豕之健者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3945:3968'>著刺時也刺不親迎也古者冕而親迎充耳瓊華乃冕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3968:3995'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-11a' );" name="003-11a" class="pb">[003-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3995:4018'>　服中之一物著與宁同人君塞門之屏也唯邦君乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4018:4041'>　樹塞門親迎宜于國門今僅在朝宁之間簡禮甚矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4041:4064'>　送夫人者訝其非禮故賦此詩充耳曰瑱懸瑱之絲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4064:4087'>　曰紞君紞五色臣三色曰素曰青曰黄謂紞也錯舉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4087:4110'>　其色之三而五可知瓊華瓊瑩瓊英則紞之所懸之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4110:4115'>　瑱也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4115:4138'>東方之日刺衰也非刺衰也刺淫也旦而彼姝入室日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4138:4160'>　夕乃出盖大夫之妻入朝而其君以無禮加之耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4160:4187'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-11b' );" name="003-11b" class="pb">[003-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4187:4210'>東方未明刺無節也周制大事用日出今東方未明已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4210:4233'>　有以失朝獲罪者故託挈壺失職以刺之顛謂衣之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4233:4256'>　領裳之要也今倒持之故曰顛倒裳衣晞者日光被</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4256:4279'>　物之名楚辭所謂晞髪是已曰未晞者日未出也栁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4279:4302'>　本賤木植諸樊圃則有主者猶挈壺之有其職也狂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4302:4325'>　夫越樊折栁猶且瞿瞿四顧恐致誚讓况晨昏大朝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4325:4348'>　之期可不以告其君乎此詩序在哀襄之間盖厲公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4348:4353'>　時矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4353:4380'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-12a' );" name="003-12a" class="pb">[003-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4380:4403'>南山刺襄公也南山崔崔宜為虎豹所宅今乃雄狐蹲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4403:4426'>　踞其間喻齊國之大而襄公以鳥獸行君臨之也葛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4426:4449'>　屨賤物猶兩兩相伍冠緌微物猶雙雙為用各有耦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4449:4472'>　也齊子已適魯矣豈吾耦乎藝麻之法須得良田而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4472:4495'>　熟耕之縱横七徧麻乃無葉婚配之際可無審處其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4495:4509'>　禮而但窮極其淫泆之心乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4509:4532'>甫田刺襄公也襄公嘗師于首止殺鄭子亹轘髙渠彌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4532:4562'>　矣又嘗伐衛而納紀季之<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0566' title='KR0566' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0566.png'/>矣又嘗與宋魯陳蔡再</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4562:4589'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-12b' );" name="003-12b" class="pb">[003-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4589:4612'>　伐衛而納惠公矣皆務大功而求伯于諸侯之事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4612:4635'>　内行不治徒負衆而恃力何能有成乎總角而弁躐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4635:4644'>　等躁蹙之喻也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4644:4667'>盧令刺荒也何所刺刺襄公也令本作獜犬之徤也鋂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4667:4690'>　者大鎖之名也北方呼黒為盧而走狗之駿者則有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4690:4713'>　韓盧環以繫項鋂以鎖之制其逸也鬈好貌偲強也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4713:4720'>　義見説文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4720:4743'>敝笱刺文姜也不獨刺文姜也正以刺魯莊公也莊公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4743:4770'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-13a' );" name="003-13a" class="pb">[003-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4770:4793'>　不能制母之欲使之瀆亂于齊如敝笱不能止細魚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4793:4816'>　耳鰥與鯤通魚禁鯤鱬鳥翼鷇卵皆其微也鄭箋訓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4816:4839'>　義是已盈車之鰥事出孔叢又因是詩而生其説耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4839:4862'>載驅齊人刺襄公也非刺襄也刺文姜也蓋莊公五年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4862:4885'>　夫人如齊師時事也薄薄輕疾貎發夕者急于赴齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4885:4908'>　即夕啓行不能待旦也豈弟訓為樂易謂其得行志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4908:4921'>　意内快于已無有阻之者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4921:4944'>猗嗟刺魯莊公也是盖莊及齊人狩于禚之詩也歴舉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4944:4971'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '003-13b' );" name="003-13b" class="pb">[003-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4971:4994'>　威儀技藝之長則其不足者自見頎而長兮言軀幹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4994:5017'>　之壯偉也抑若揚兮言威儀之矜莊也美目而下皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='5017:5040'>　述其善射之狀也目上為名謂張目注視而發矢也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='5040:5063'>　方射之時無所用舞舞則選兮謂射耦也射禮王六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5063:5086'>　耦諸侯四耦猶舞佾列焉射者搢三挾一故稱四矢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5086:5089'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5089:5092'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5092:5099'>　詩故卷三</span><br/>
</p>
